      "content": "hey, my stomach has been hurting really bad for a few hours now. it started feeling weird around my belly button but now it's moved down to the right side and it's super sharp. i think it might just be bad gas or maybe just really bad period cramps? i'm trying to sleep but the pain is keeping me up. can i just take some extra strength ibuprofen or maybe even some oxy if i have any left over to help me sleep through it? i dont want to go to the er if i dont have to",
