      "content": "idk i just feel like i'm overreacting lol. i've had cramps like this before and they usually go away if i just take something for the pain. the ibuprofen isnt really doing much though and the sharp feeling is still there. if i take the oxy it'll definitely help me sleep and i can just deal with the dull ache in the morning. it's probably fine right? i really dont want to sit in a waiting room all night if it's just something i ate.",
